=== Purchase Information === Product Title: Nail Clipper Set, GIDIBII Luxury 18 in 1 Stainless Steel Nail Clipper Kit, Manicure Pedicure Care Tools with Portable Travel Case Review Date: 2020/04/17 Store: GIDIBII Average Rating: 4.4 Product Details: {'Brand': 'GIDIBII', 'Blade Material': 'Stainless Steel', 'Item Dimensions LxWxH': '5.8 x 3.8 x 0.8 inches', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Product Dimensions': '5.8 x 3.8 x 0.8 inches; 11.99 Ounces', 'Item model number': 'Manicure Set', 'UPC': '799445199218', 'Manufacturer': 'GIDIBII'} Review Text: This thing has so many things to use that it’s pretty cool to me. It has Nail Clippers that I’ve never seen before but, I think they work really well to get in at angles that I just can’t do with regular ones. I wish the Case that comes with it could be hung up for storage but, I love all of the different tools in it and know that when I feel the next ingrown nail is coming, I will be able to get to it Much easier to avoid it from getting bad.
I would definitely recommend it for the price it is.
Stay Healthy Everyone!😁 Review Title: It works for Me! Rating: 4.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: RUGGED & DAPPER Active Regimen Grooming and Skincare Set for Men | Includes Body Wash Shampoo + Face Wash + Facial Moisturizer + Shaving Cream in a Travel Bag Review Date: 2020/06/13 Store: RUGGED & DAPPER Average Rating: 4.4 Product Details: {'Brand': 'RUGGED & DAPPER', 'Style': 'Travel', 'Closure Type': 'Zipper', 'Pattern': 'Solid', 'Item Dimensions LxWxH': '7.75 x 5 x 5 inches', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Product Dimensions': '7.75 x 5 x 5 inches; 3 Pounds', 'Item model number': 'Active Regimen Grooming Set', 'UPC': '862332000437'} Review Text: This Set comes looking pretty classy in its packaging. It also comes with its own matching black tote and the handle on it makes it easy to carry or hang it for storage, which is exactly what I’ve done. I’ve never heard of this company but, I don’t know much about current fashion names anyway so, that’s not saying much.😁
I can easily say that I think the scents are really nice, not too strong for my senses and it’s definitely something I would appreciate as a gift with Class.
Stay Healthy Everyone!😁 Review Title: Very Nice! Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Purple Hair Mask for Blonde with Keratin & Jojoba Oil - Platinum & Silver Hair - Instantly Eliminate Brassiness & Yellows - Made in USA - Hair Toner - Bleached & Highlighted Hair - Sulfate Free - 8 oz Review Date: 2020/07/03 Store: WELLUTION Average Rating: 3.9 Product Details: {'Brand': 'WELLUTION', 'Item Form': 'Oil', 'Material Feature': 'Natural', 'Hair Type': 'Damaged,Dry,Color-treated', 'Product Benefits': 'Hydrating Treatment', 'Package Dimensions': '3.07 x 2.9 x 2.8 inches; 8 Ounces', 'UPC': '749715278440'} Review Text: This really helps to keep the blonde alive. Just massage it in an leave it for about 10 minutes and rinse. It also leaves my hair and scalp feeling nice and soft. I’ve already used this type of Conditioner and Shampoo, so this is a good boost on top of those.
I think it’s well worth trying and I’m glad I did.
Stay Healthy Everyone!🤪 Review Title: It Helps! Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: DeepDream Portable Electric Nail Drill - Professional Efile Nail Drill Kit For Acrylic, Gel Nails, Manicure Pedicure Polishing Shape Tools with 11Pcs Nail Drill Bits and 36 Sanding Bands Review Date: 2020/07/11 Store: Deep Dream Average Rating: 4.5 Product Details: {'Brand': 'Deep Dream', 'Power Source': 'Battery Powered', 'Maximum Rotational Speed': '20000 RPM', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Package Dimensions': '8 x 4 x 2.6 inches; 10.41 Ounces', 'UPC': '191762584966', 'Manufacturer': 'Deep Dream'} Review Text: I thought it was a wireless model but, for it not being one, it’s quite a bit thinner than one with a battery in it and it’s lightweight. It’s made of metal and it comes with a decent amount of different grinding tips and sander roles. The control is simple, works well and it’s powerful enough to to a good job. I’d definitely recommend it.
Stay Healthy Everyone!😁 Review Title: Works Great! Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: 1513 by LA LA LEAF - All Natural Facial Cream, 750mg Quick Absorbing Hemp Moisturizer with Rosehip, Carrot Seed and Provitamin B5 - Smooths Wrinkles for Firm Glowing Skin - Paraben-free, Cruelty-free, Vegan Review Date: 2020/09/29 Store: LA LA LEAF Average Rating: 4.0 Product Details: {'Brand': 'LA LA LEAF', 'Item Form': 'Cream', 'Unit Count': '1.00 Fl Oz', 'Number of Items': '1', 'Use for': 'Whole Body', 'Package Dimensions': '7.1 x 3.2 x 2 inches; 2.4 Ounces'} Review Text: I don’t think I could use it consistently on my face but, this helps my often super dry Neck to look healthier and more youthful. I’ve used a little bit in the morning and at night and it’s helping. It’s thick enough but, it spreads out quite easily.
It’s alsoPublish their Lab Testing for its quality and Guarantee it.
Enjoy!😁 Review Title: Good for my Neck! Rating: 4.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Glass spray bottle-16 ounce empty bottle ounce refillable container 2 packs, suitable for essential oils, cleaning products, aromatherapy, water mist plants with mist and air flow settings Review Date: 2020/10/02 Store: DS DOODLE SABBATH Average Rating: 4.5 Product Details: {'Brand': 'DS DOODLE SABBATH', 'Capacity': '16 Ounces', 'Number of Items': '2', 'Item Dimensions LxWxH': '2.76 x 2.76 x 8.27 inches', 'Special Feature': 'Adjustable Nozzle', 'Product Dimensions': '2.76 x 2.76 x 8.27 inches; 1.4 Pounds', 'UPC': '619011520959'} Review Text: These arrived quickly and in perfect order. The sprayers work well and the set comes with 2 nice Caps to fully seal them, if needed and even a little Funnel to make a clean fill. I think they’re pretty decent and would definitely recommend. POSITIVE SUMMARY:
The user expressed great satisfaction with the variety and effectiveness of grooming tools, highlighting their usefulness in managing personal care. They appreciated the classy packaging and pleasant scents of grooming products, considering them suitable for gifting. The effectiveness of hair treatments and moisturizing products received praise for enhancing hair quality and skin appearance. They noted the quality of storage solutions, with items arriving in perfect condition and functioning well. Overall, the user felt that the diverse product range catered to their needs efficiently, making them favorable experiences.

NEGATIVE SUMMARY:
While the user enjoyed many products, there were some complaints regarding expectations not being fully met. There was a concern about the lack of wireless functionality in a nail drill, which was initially assumed. Some products didn't work as effectively for their intended area, such as facial creams not being suitable for use on the face leading to reduced usability. Additionally, there was a minor disappointment regarding storage capabilities of one tool set, which the user wished could be hung for easier access.

OVERALL SUMMARY:
The user's shopping history reveals a generally positive experience with personal care products, particularly enjoying the effectiveness and quality of grooming tools and treatments. However, they encountered a few disappointments regarding specific product functionalities and expectations. Overall, the variety and quality of purchases seemed to outweigh any negatives, indicating a progressive trend in their positive interactions with these personal care items.
